I>Processi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ns and Perambulations,</HI> b<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">t <HI>the obser|v<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">tions of Holy|dayes, repeating the L<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">tany, th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> lik<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> form<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> in the G<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">mm<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">n-Prayer, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">he bowing at the name of Ies<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">, receiving the Sacram<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">nt upo<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> kn<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">e,</HI> are reckon<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">d up in the sam<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> p<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ge.</NOTE> oth<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">r things which
