<P><NOTE PLACE="marg"><HI>Guilty men must keep their secrets, or not be angry that they are known.</HI></NOTE>But by the way let me tell you, that you were ne|ver in <HI>my Thoughts,</HI> when I expressed my <HI>Dislike</HI> of <HI>Sequestrations.</HI> I never knew you had any, untill you <HI>told</HI> me: Nor had I knowne it to <HI>this houre,</HI> had you but kept your owne <HI>counsell.</HI> So little Reason had you to use me with so much <HI>Bitternesse</HI> and <HI>Virulence</HI> in divers Books. But <HI>worser</HI> dealing then from <HI>your selfe</HI> (though not in print) I have h<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">d from a <HI>Mi|nister</HI>
