as if it might be sai'd of his opinion, as <HI>Austine</HI> speaks of discretion, Tolle hanc, &amp; virtus vitium erit. <HI>ib. p.</HI> 17. <HI>l.</HI> 18. <HI>&amp;c.</HI></P>
